SIMPLE: nicker_nut
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nicker nut
<hw>Nick"er nut`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>A rounded seed, rather smaller
than a nutmeg, having a hard smooth shell, and a yellowish or bluish
color. The seeds grow in the prickly pods of tropical, woody climbers of
the genus <gen>Caesalpinia</gen>. <spn>Caesalpinia Bonduc</spn> has
yellowish seeds; <spn>Caesalpinia Bonducella</spn>, bluish gray.</def>
<altsp>[Spelt also <asp>neckar nut</asp>, <asp>nickar
nut</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nicker tree</ent>⟦br⟧
